Quote:  52. <i>Nestor notabilis</i>, Gould. Mountain or Green parrot, Sheep-killer, Kea, Kia, Keha, Keo, Kaieo. - By all these names is this troublesome bird known by the highland shepherds and sheep musterers in alpine districts from Lakes Wanaka and Hawea to the river Rangitata.
Notes:   (T.H. Potts)

